                <Property name="text" type="java.lang.String" value="The organization serves as a platform that supports students&#x2019; academic and personal growth&#xa;through various programs and activities. It encourages leadership, collaboration, and active &#xa;participation among students. Through its initiatives, it helps students develop  skills and build &#xa;connections that are valuable for their future careers."/>
